			<div class="ibox-info"><a href="Expressing_quality" title="Expressing quality">Expressing quality</a> </div>
		</li>
		<li class="ibox-keywords clearfix">
			<div class="ibox-label">Keywords</div>
			<div class="ibox-info"><a href="一" title="一">一</a>, <a href="一方面" title="一方面">一方面</a>, <a href="方面" title="方面">方面</a></div>
		</li>
		
	</ul>
	<div class="ibox-image"><a href="./File:Chinese-grammar-wiki-yi.jpg" class="image"><img alt="Chinese-grammar-wiki-yi.jpg" src="https://resources.allsetlearning.com/gramwiki/images/thumb/9/99/Chinese-grammar-wiki-yi.jpg/300px-Chinese-grammar-wiki-yi.jpg" decoding="async" width="300" height="300" srcset="https://resources.allsetlearning.com/gramwiki/images/thumb/9/99/Chinese-grammar-wiki-yi.jpg/450px-Chinese-grammar-wiki-yi.jpg 1.5x, https://resources.allsetlearning.com/gramwiki/images/thumb/9/99/Chinese-grammar-wiki-yi.jpg/600px-Chinese-grammar-wiki-yi.jpg 2x" /></a></div>
</div> 
<p>When talking about various aspects of a situation, 一方面⋯⋯， (另)一方面⋯⋯ (yī fāngmiàn..., (lìng) yī fāngmiàn...) can be used in a way similar to how "on one hand..., on the other hand..." is used in English. 
</p>
<div id="toc" class="toc"><input type="checkbox" role="button" id="toctogglecheckbox" class="toctogglecheckbox" style="display:none" /><div class="toctitle" lang="en" dir="ltr"><h2>Contents</h2><span class="toctogglespan"><label class="toctogglelabel" for="toctogglecheckbox"></label></span></div>
<ul>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-1"><a href="ASGCWHNF#Structure"><span class="tocnumber">1</span> <span class="toctext">Structure</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-2"><a href="ASGCWHNF#Examples"><span class="tocnumber">2</span> <span class="toctext">Examples</span></a></li>
